Invocation Name: dogs watch
des:
Dogs Watch will keep intruders away by playing sounds of dogs barking, growling, and snarling while you're away.

Burglars will likely avoid your home if they hear angry dogs inside!

These dogs sounds will keep you safe!!!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
